{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"751cfa5adb","title":"在政治局会议上的讲话提纲","origin":"","is_range_date":false,"dates":[{"id":"6b3a926a9d","index":0,"year":1953,"month":6,"day":15,"articleId":"751cfa5adb"}],"tags":[{"id":"994fc035d4","name":"工业战线","type":"主题/事件"},{"id":"dd2b275f6c","name":"毛泽东","type":"人物"},{"id":"e23dcf99fa","name":"发言","type":"文稿类型"},{"id":"e759231f2d","name":"农业战线","type":"主题/事件"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"maoquanji33","name":"毛泽东全集第33卷","internal":false,"official":false,"type":"pdf","author":"张迪杰","files":"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/banned-historical-archives/banned-historical-archives0/main/mao-quanji/33-OCR.pdf"}],"authors":[{"id":"261e5467ec","name":"毛泽东"}]},"publication_details":{"maoquanji33":{"comments":[],"contents":[{"id":"d10e8c78f5","type":"title","text":"在政治局会议上的讲话提纲","index":0,"publicationId":"maoquanji33","articleId":"751cfa5adb"},{"id":"1f490b9f29","type":"paragraph","text":"总路线是照耀一切工作的灯塔","index":1,"publicationId":"maoquanji33","articleId":"751cfa5adb"},{"id":"fce53684e5","type":"paragraph","text":"有所不同和一视同仁，公私兼顾、劳资两利和发展生产、繁荣经济，前者管着后者。","index":2,"publicationId":"maoquanji33","articleId":"751cfa5adb"},{"id":"81240f469b","type":"paragraph","text":"几点错误观点：（一）确立新民主主义的社会秩序；（二）由新民主主义走向社会主义；（三）确保私有财产。","index":3,"publicationId":"maoquanji33","articleId":"751cfa5adb"},{"id":"f4bc9bd1de","type":"paragraph","text":"党的任务是在十年至十五年或者更多一些时间内，基本上完成国家工业化和社会主义的改造。","index":4,"publicationId":"maoquanji33","articleId":"751cfa5adb"},{"id":"78c7500060","type":"paragraph","text":"所谓社会主义改造的部分：（一）农业；（二）手工业；（三）资本主义企业。","index":5,"publicationId":"maoquanji33","articleId":"751cfa5adb"},{"id":"f2db247bf0","type":"paragraph","text":"逐步","index":6,"publicationId":"maoquanji33","articleId":"751cfa5adb"},{"id":"ecf1cc26b4","type":"paragraph","text":"对于将资本主义逐步过渡到社会主义的认识——社会主义成分是可以逐年增长的，资产阶级的基本部分是可教育的。","index":7,"publicationId":"maoquanji33","articleId":"751cfa5adb"}],"page":{"id":"9d6e0d2500","publicationId":"maoquanji33","articleId":"751cfa5adb","start":199,"end":199}}}},"__N_SSG":true}